## 数据流架构（当前版本）

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["29个信源<br/>直连/Singbox/RSSHub"] -->|拉取| B["RSSCollector<br/>collector容器"]
    B -->|PENDING + 市场快照| DB[("PostgreSQL<br/>intelligence表")]
    B -->|Redis PUBLISH| R["Redis<br/>alphasignal:new_intelligence"]
    R -->|即时唤醒| C["AlphaEngine<br/>worker容器"]
    DB -->|get_pending| C
    C --> C1["EventClusterer<br/>pg_trgm聚类"]
    C1 --> C2["NewsDeduplicator<br/>SimHash+pgvector"]
    C2 --> C3["AI分析<br/>DeepSeek主力/Gemini备用"]
    C3 -->|含 DXY/Oil/TNX 宏观上下文| C3
    C3 -->|COMPLETED| DB
    C3 -->|urgency≥7| D["推送<br/>Bark/Email"]
    DB -->|1h/4h后| E["BacktestEngine<br/>价格回填"]
    E -->|准确率回填| DB
```

